@deleted-role Welcome to the final cheesy game we have setup for you this season! This one is for Hungry Spectators only! The Edgic Game A lot of spectators love seeing the edgic charts, some even make their own for the season and we love to see that level of participation. In fact, we loved it so much we decided to make it a game! We will provide you all with an edgic template that will match what we use for production and each episode you can submit an image of what you think the players edgics will be! You can earn three points per player per episode. If you match the visibility you get one point, if you match the tone you get another point and if you match the rating you can earn a point! The closer you are to the overall production edgic, the more points you will get! Rules Each episode before we release the OFFICIAL edgic you can submit an image (or just a chart, whatever works best) of your edgic for the players that episode. If your edgic for a player matches in someway to the production edgic you get points! The player with the largest total at the end of the season will win! The Prize $10 USD for 1st $0 USD for anything else, we only give prizes to WINNERS The Spreadsheet https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16DpMNGxamEdPbLWCXn9nLY5DqsjB_04VGlAwA4Z0Oaw/edit#gid=799323222 (edited)
